<!-- 定義及症狀 -->
'''骨盆腔發炎'''（Pelvic inflammatory disease，PID）也稱為'''盆腔炎'''，指的是女性[[子宮|子宮]]或[[輸卵管|輸卵管]]受到[[感染|感染]]的情形，有些定義也包含[[卵巢|卵巢]]感染<ref name=Mit2013>{{cite journal|last1=Mitchell|first1=C|last2=Prabhu|first2=M|title=Pelvic inflammatory disease: current concepts in pathogenesis, diagnosis and treatment.|journal=Infectious disease clinics of North America|date=December 2013|volume=27|issue=4|pages=793–809|pmid=24275271}}</ref>。骨盆腔發炎時常無明顯的症狀<ref name=CDC2014Sym>{{cite web|title=Pelvic Inflammatory Disease (PID) Clinical Manifestations and Sequelae|url=http://www2a.cdc.gov/stdtraining/self-study/pid/pid_clinical_self_study_from_cdc.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=21 February 2015|date=October 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222022835/http://www2a.cdc.gov/stdtraining/self-study/pid/pid_clinical_self_study_from_cdc.html|archive-date=2015-02-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>可能病徵有下腹痛、[[陰道分泌物|陰道分泌物]]、[[發燒|發燒]]、排尿時[[排尿困難|尿道有灼熱感]]、[[性交疼痛|性交疼痛]]和不規律的流血<ref name=Mit2013/><ref name=CDC2014Sym/>。骨盆腔發炎會導致長期的併發症，例如：[[不孕症|不孕症]]、[[異位妊娠|異位妊娠]]和{{le|慢性骨盆疼痛|chronic pelvic pain}}<ref name=Mit2013/>。

<!-- 病因及診斷 -->
大約75~90%的病例可以在感染處發現[[淋球菌|淋球菌]]或[[砂眼披衣菌|砂眼披衣菌]]<!-- <ref name=Mit2013/> -->，但時常有其他不同種細菌同時感染<ref name=Mit2013/>。如果[[淋病|淋病]]和[[披衣菌感染|披衣菌感染]]的患者未積極接受治療，大約分別有40%和10%會惡化為骨盆腔發炎<ref name=Mit2013/><ref name=WHO2012>{{cite web|author1=World Health Organization|title=Global incidence and prevalence of selected curable sexually transmitted infections - 2008|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/75181/1/9789241503839_eng.pdf|website=who.int|accessdate=22 February 2015|pages=2, 19|date=2012|archive-date=2015-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319011717/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/75181/1/9789241503839_eng.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該疾病危險因子通常和[[性傳染病|性病]]相似，包括大量的性伴侶和[[藥物濫用|藥物濫用]]<!-- <ref name=Mit2013/> -->。{{le|陰道灌洗|Vaginal douching}}也會增加罹病風險<!-- <ref name=Mit2013/> -->。典型的診斷是基於目前的徵兆和症狀<!-- <ref name=Mit2013/> -->，因此若育齡婦女有下腹疼痛，需將骨盆腔發炎列入可能疾病<!-- <ref name=Mit2013/> -->。直接的診斷是藉由[[手術|手術]]中觀看輸卵管和[[膿|膿]]<!-- <ref name=Mit2013/> -->。超音波也對診斷很有幫助<ref name=Mit2013/>。

<!-- 預防及治療 -->
預防方法包含：[[禁慾|禁慾]]、減少性伴侶，以及正確使用保險套<ref>{{cite web|title=Pelvic Inflammatory Disease (PID) Patient Counseling and Education|url=http://www2a.cdc.gov/stdtraining/self-study/pid/pid_patient_counseling_self_study_from_cdc.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=21 February 2015|date=October 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222021120/http://www2a.cdc.gov/stdtraining/self-study/pid/pid_patient_counseling_self_study_from_cdc.html|archive-date=2015-02-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。對於具有披衣菌感染風險的女性進行預防性篩檢和治療，也能降低骨盆腔發炎的機會<ref name=CDC2014Pub/>。骨盆腔發炎一旦確診一般建議進行治療<ref name=Mit2013/> ，且性伴侶也需同時進行相關的檢查及治療<ref name=CDC2014Pub>{{cite web|title=Pelvic Inflammatory Disease (PID) Partner Management and Public Health Measures|url=http://www2a.cdc.gov/stdtraining/self-study/pid/pid_partner_management_self_study_from_cdc.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=21 February 2015|date=October 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911072306/https://www2a.cdc.gov/stdtraining/self-study/pid/pid_partner_management_self_study_from_cdc.html|archive-date=2017-09-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。症狀輕微者可以注射一劑[[頭孢曲松|頭孢曲松]][[抗細菌藥|抗生素]]後，口服兩周的[[多西環素|多西環素]]或[[甲硝唑|甲硝唑]]<!-- <ref name=CDC2010Tx/> -->。重症者如果三天後未改善則需考慮靜脈注射抗生素<ref name=CDC2010Tx>{{cite web|title=2010 STD Treatment Guidelines Pelvic Inflammatory Disease|url=http://www.cdc.gov/std/treatment/2010/pid.htm|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=22 February 2015|date=August 15, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222002803/http://www.cdc.gov/std/treatment/2010/pid.htm|archive-date=2015-02-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

<!-- 流行病學及歷史 -->
2008年全球有1.06億人感染衣原菌，另外有1.06億人感染淋病<ref name=WHO2012/>，但骨盆腔發炎的人數並不清楚<ref name=Esch2008/>，估計每年約有1.5%的年輕女性有骨盆腔發炎的症狀<ref name=Esch2008>{{cite journal|author1=Eschenbach, D|title=Acute Pelvic Inflammatory Disease|journal=Glob. libr. women's med.|date=2008|doi=10.3843/GLOWM.10029|issn=1756-2228}}</ref>，美國估計每年有一百人受到骨盆腔發炎的影響<ref name=CDC2014Epi>{{cite web|title=Self-Study STD Modules for Clinicians - Pelvic Inflammatory Disease (PID) Next Centers for Disease Control and Prevention Your Online Source for Credible Health Information CDC Home Footer Separator Rectangle Epidemiology|url=http://www2a.cdc.gov/stdtraining/self-study/pid/pid_epidemiology_self_study_from_cdc.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=21 February 2015|date=October 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911071159/https://www2a.cdc.gov/stdtraining/self-study/pid/pid_epidemiology_self_study_from_cdc.html|archive-date=2017-09-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。1970年代一種稱為{{le|達康盾|Dalkon Shield}}的[[子宮環|子宮環]]會增加骨盆腔發炎的機率<!-- <ref name=Mit2013/> -->，現在使用的子宮環在使用一個月之後，不會造成骨盆腔發炎<ref name=Mit2013/>。

